<h1>NEW USER FORM COMPONENT</h1>

<header>
  <h2>Create New User</h2>
  <div class="clear"></div>
</header>

<section class="newUser">
  <form id="newUser">
    Name:
    {{input type="text" value=newUserName classNames="displayName"}}
    (PoW) Username:
    {{input type="text" value=newUserUsername classNames="userName" key-press='checkUsername'}}
    Authorized:
    {{input type="checkbox" name=newUserAuthorized checked=newUserAuthorized classNames="isAuthorized"}}
    <button class="newUser" {{action 'newUser'}}>add user</button>
  </form>
</section> 
<p>Users are automatically created on log in, however if you want to create them ahead of time (so that they are authorized) you can do that here.</p>

{{yield}}